AND JEFFREY CAN'T.

32:00.186 --> 32:01.954
>> I'M ACTING
IN MY CLIENT'S BEST INTERESTS.

32:01.988 --> 32:03.222
>> YOUR CLIENT HAS
AS MUCH BUSINESS

32:03.255 --> 32:05.357
ON A WITNESS STAND
AS I DO RIDING IN A RODEO.

32:05.391 --> 32:09.228
ONLY A HORSE'S ASS WOULD IGNORE
HIS DIMINISHED MENTAL CAPACITY.

32:09.261 --> 32:10.696
>> YOU'RE OUT OF LINE,
YOUR HONOR.

32:10.729 --> 32:13.732
>> AND YOU ARE A DISGRACE
TO THE DEFENSE BAR, MR. GRANGER.

32:13.765 --> 32:17.169
AND IF YOU DON'T GET
YOUR ACT IN LINE,

32:17.203 --> 32:19.171
