AND REPORT YOU

32:19.205 --> 32:20.272
TO THE DISCIPLINARY COMMITTEE.

32:20.306 --> 32:22.308
NOW GET OUT.

32:25.644 --> 32:27.279
NOT YOU, ALEX.

32:27.313 --> 32:29.581
YOU'RE NOT BLAMELESS
IN THIS.

32:29.615 --> 32:30.749
>> THE PEOPLE DON'T HAVE
THE BURDEN TO PROVE

32:30.782 --> 32:32.651
THE DEFENDANT INCOMPETENT
TO STAND TRIAL.

32:32.684 --> 32:34.653
>> NO, YOU HAVE
A BIGGER BURDEN.

32:34.686 --> 32:36.188
TO SEE THAT JUSTICE IS DONE.

32:36.222 --> 32:39.558
>> I AM.
JEFFREY LYNWOOD KILLED A MAN.

32:39.591 --> 32:42.128
>> JEFFREY LYNWOOD HAS THE MIND
OF A CHILD.

32:42.161 --> 32:43.762
HE CAN'T STAND UP
FOR HIMSELF.

32:43.795 --> 32:47.399
VIOLATING HIS RIGHTS
ISN'T JUSTICE.

32:47.433 --> 32:48.700
>> YOUR HONOR,
WITH ALL DUE RESPECT,

32:48.734 --> 32:50.702
WE AREN'T IN YOUR CONSTITUTIONAL
LAW CLASS ANYMORE.

32:50.736 --> 32:52.038
THIS IS THE REAL WORLD.

32:54.273 --> 32:56.508
>> I KNOW YOU'VE SEEN
MORE OF THE REAL WORLD

32:56.542 --> 32:57.509
THAN ANYBODY SHOULD HAVE TO.

32:57.543 --> 33:00.579
IT TOOK GUTS TO COME BACK.

33:00.612 --> 33:01.580
AND I'M GLAD YOU DID.

33:01.613 --> 33:04.516
BUT YOU CAN'T AFFORD TO FORGET

33:04.550 --> 33:08.254
WHY YOU BECAME AN ADA
IN THE FIRST PLACE.

33:08.287 --> 33:12.191
THE ALEXANDRA CABOT
I REMEMBER...

33:12.224 --> 33:16.195
WOULDN'T EVEN CONSIDER
RAILROADING THIS POOR YOUNG MAN.

33:22.301 --> 33:23.469
>> YOU WERE RIGHT.

33:23.502 --> 33:26.405
I WAS OUT FOR BLOOD.

33:26.438 --> 33:28.240
>> AND I WAS ABOUT TO CALL YOU.

33:28.274 --> 33:30.576
I THINK I KNOW WHAT'S REALLY
WRONG WITH JEFFREY.

33:30.609 --> 33:33.345
>> WHAT DIFFERENCE DOES IT MAKE?
INCOMPETENT IS INCOMPETENT.

33:33.379 --> 33:36.282
>> THE TRAGEDY IS,
IT DIDN'T HAVE TO BE THAT WAY.

33:36.315 --> 33:38.217
>> HOW CAN YOU BE SURE?

33:38.250 --> 33:41.153
>> WE NEED TO TALK
TO HIS MOTHER.

33:42.454 --> 33:44.056
>> I CAN'T TALK TO YOU.

33:44.090 --> 33:48.360
>> MRS. LYNWOOD...
PLEASE.

33:55.834 --> 33:57.269
WHEN JEFFREY WAS A BABY,

33:57.303 --> 33:59.071
DID HE HIT ALL
HIS DEVELOPMENTAL MILESTONES?

33:59.105 --> 34:02.541
>> YEAH, HE WAS FINE
UNTIL HE WAS FIVE.

34:02.574 --> 34:03.675
>> AND THEN WHAT HAPPENED?

34:03.709 --> 34:04.776
>> HE HAD A SEIZURE.

34:04.810 --> 34:09.548
AND HIS BRAIN SWELLED.

34:09.581 --> 34:11.617
AND WE THOUGHT
HE WAS GONNA DIE.

34:14.486 --> 34:17.289
WHEN HE FINALLY RECOVERED,
HE JUST...

34:17.323 --> 34:20.392
HE WASN'T THE SAME.

34:20.426 --> 34:23.462
DR. KEPPLER SAID THAT IT WAS
A MIRACLE THAT HE SURVIVED.

34:23.495 --> 34:25.364
>> DID HE KNOW
WHAT CAUSED THE SEIZURE?

34:25.397 --> 34:27.699
>> MM-HMM.
HE SAID IT WAS EPILEPSY.

34:27.733 --> 34:31.203
>> DR. KEPPLER MISSED
JEFFREY'S PICA.

34:31.237 --> 34:33.639
>> WHAT IS PICA?

34:33.672 --> 34:34.640
>> IT'S A RARE NEUROLOGICAL
DISORDER

34:34.673 --> 34:36.642
IN WHICH A PERSON EATS OBJECTS
OTHER THAN FOOD,

34:36.675 --> 34:38.244
LIKE WHEN JEFFREY WAS CHEWING
ON THE PENCIL

34:38.277 --> 34:40.379
IN COURT.

34:40.412 --> 34:41.780
>> THAT'S WHY
WE COULDN'T MAKE HIM

34:41.813 --> 34:43.115
STOP PUTTING THINGS
IN HIS MOUTH.

34:43.149 --> 34:44.816
>> WHAT KINDS OF THINGS?

34:44.850 --> 34:46.352
>> WHATEVER HE COULD GET
HIS HANDS ON.

34:46.385 --> 34:49.288
>> IS THERE ANY CHANCE
YOU KEPT SOMETHING?

34:51.290 --> 34:52.258
>> YES.

34:52.291 --> 34:55.227
HIS LITTLE TOY CARS.

34:55.261 --> 34:58.297
MY HUSBAND CAME HOME
FROM WORK ONE NIGHT

34:58.330 --> 35:00.266
WITH DOZENS OF THEM.

35:00.299 --> 35:01.600
>> AND TWO DAYS LATER,

35:01.633 --> 35:04.436
JEFFREY'D LICKED THE PAINT
OFF EVERY ONE OF THEM.

35:04.470 --> 35:07.539
SAID THEY TASTED
LIKE SWEET AND SOUR CANDY.

35:07.573 --> 35:09.841
>> VIRGINIA.
DID YOU LET THEM IN HERE?

35:09.875 --> 35:11.777
>> YES, THEY'RE HERE
TO HELP JEFFREY.

35:11.810 --> 35:12.878
>> NO, THEY'RE NOT.

35:12.911 --> 35:14.746
THEY'RE HERE
TO SLAP A LABEL ON HIM.

35:14.780 --> 35:16.715
>> WE KNOW
WHAT'S WRONG WITH YOUR SON.

35:16.748 --> 35:18.384
>> SO DO I.
HE'S A LITTLE SLOW.

35:18.417 --> 35:19.751
>> WAKE UP, CLIVE.

35:19.785 --> 35:24.790
JEFFREY'S DEVELOPMENTALLY
DELAYED.

35:24.823 --> 35:25.891
HE'S NEVER GONNA BE
THE PERFECT CHILD

35:25.924 --> 35:30.496
YOU ALWAYS WANTED.

35:37.636 --> 35:40.672
>> HE WAS PERFECTLY FINE
WHEN HE WAS A BABY.

35:40.706 --> 35:43.809
>> HE WASN'T BORN
THIS WAY.

35:43.842 --> 35:45.411
AND I CAN PROVE IT.

35:48.647 --> 35:50.349
AFTER SEEING JEFF EAT THE PENCIL
IN COURT YESTERDAY,

35:50.382 --> 35:52.384
I ORDERED AN MRI OF HIS BRAIN.

35:52.418 --> 35:55.354
THESE RED SPOTS INDICATE AREAS
OF MISSING GRAY MATTER.

35:55.387 --> 35:58.224
>> MISSING?
HOW?

35:58.257 --> 36:00.459
>> CHRONIC LEAD POISONING
PREVENTED JEFF'S BRAIN CELLS

36:00.492 --> 36:01.460
FROM GROWING.

36:01.493 --> 36:03.795
>> LEAD POISONING?

36:03.829 --> 36:05.197
ARE YOU SURE?

36:05.231 --> 36:06.465
>> MOST KIDS GET IT
FROM BREATHING DUST

36:06.498 --> 36:07.799
FROM DECAYING LEAD PAINT.

36:07.833 --> 36:11.503
BUT KIDS WITH PICA
ARE ALSO AT HIGH RISK.

36:11.537 --> 36:14.406
LEAD BUILDUP IN JEFF'S BODY
PROBABLY CAUSED HIS SEIZURE.

36:14.440 --> 36:15.907
>> AND STUDIES LINK
LEAD POISONING IN KIDS

36:15.941 --> 36:18.210
TO VIOLENT BEHAVIOR
WHEN THEY BECOME ADULTS.

36:18.244 --> 36:20.579
>> ARE YOU SAYING THIS EXCUSES
WHAT JEFFREY DID?

36:20.612 --> 36:22.648
>> JEFF'S ANTERIOR CINGULATE
CORTEX,

36:22.681 --> 36:24.950
THE EMOTION AND DECISION-MAKING
CENTER OF THE BRAIN,

36:24.983 --> 36:26.252
IS BADLY DAMAGED.

36:26.285 --> 36:28.854
WITH THE RIGHT PROVOCATION,

36:28.887 --> 36:30.389
THAT'S LIKE TAKING THE MUZZLE
OFF A RABID DOG.

36:30.422 --> 36:32.991
>> IT EXPLAINS WHY HE REACTED
SO VIOLENTLY

36:33.024 --> 36:34.460
WHEN DR. KEPPLER CALLED HIM
NAMES.

36:34.493 --> 36:38.797
>> KEPPLER NEVER TESTED JEFFREY
FOR LEAD

36:38.830 --> 36:40.499
BEFORE OR AFTER THE SEIZURE,
DID HE?

36:40.532 --> 36:44.002
>> NO.
>> HE NEVER EVEN MENTIONED IT.

36:44.035 --> 36:49.841
SO THAT BASTARD VICTIMIZED
MY SON TWICE.

36:55.581 --> 36:56.615
>> HI, MOM.
HI, DAD.

36:56.648 --> 36:58.750
>> HI.
HOW YOU DOING, KIDDO?

36:58.784 --> 37:01.219
>> I DON'T LIKE IT HERE.
THE PEOPLE AREN'T NICE.

37:03.021 --> 37:05.857
WHY ARE YOU CRYING, DADDY?

37:17.503 --> 37:18.970
>> BECAUSE I DIDN'T HELP YOU
ENOUGH,

37:19.004 --> 37:21.840
AND I'M SO SORRY.

37:21.873 --> 37:25.444
I'M SO SORRY.

37:27.546 --> 37:30.416
>> IT'S OKAY, DAD.

37:30.449 --> 37:31.650
I DID A BAD THING.

37:38.557 --> 37:41.593
>> SO I GUESS THIS MEANS
WE'RE NOT GOING BACK TO TRIAL.

37:41.627 --> 37:44.296
>> OH, YES, WE ARE.

37:46.632 --> 37:48.500
SIR, COULD YOU PLEASE STATE
YOUR NAME, POSITION,

37:48.534 --> 37:50.536
AND WHY YOU'RE HERE
FOR THE RECORD.

37:50.569 --> 37:53.305
>> MICHAEL ROWAN, PRESIDENT
AND CHIEF EXECUTIVE OFFICER

37:53.339 --> 37:54.573
OF ROWAN TOYS INCORPORATED.

37:54.606 --> 37:55.941
YOU ASKED ME TO APPEAR

37:55.974 --> 37:57.208
AS AN EXPERT WITNESS
ON OUR PRODUCTS.

37:57.242 --> 38:00.479
>> THE DEFENSE STIPULATES TO THE
WITNESS'S EXPERTISE, YOUR HONOR.

38:00.512 --> 38:02.348
>> THE PEOPLE'S THREE
AND FOUR, YOUR HONOR.

38:02.381 --> 38:04.316
MR. ROWAN,
WHAT ARE THESE?

38:04.350 --> 38:05.584
>> OUR MINI ICE CREAM TRUCK.

38:05.617 --> 38:07.653
STILL A BIG SELLER.

38:07.686 --> 38:08.987
PAINT'S MISSING ON THAT ONE.

38:09.020 --> 38:10.456
>> THAT'S BECAUSE
JEFFREY LYNWOOD CHEWED IT OFF,

38:10.489 --> 38:12.791
WHICH THE DEFENSE CLAIMS
GAVE HIM LEAD POISONING.

38:12.824 --> 38:13.725
>> THAT'S IMPOSSIBLE.

38:13.759 --> 38:15.461
LEAD-BASED PAINT HAS BEEN BANNED
FROM TOYS

38:15.494 --> 38:17.629
IN THIS COUNTRY
SINCE 1978.

38:17.663 --> 38:19.465
WE HAVEN'T USED IT SINCE.

38:19.498 --> 38:20.499
>> WHAT ABOUT ON THE TOYS
YOU MAKE OVERSEAS?

38:20.532 --> 38:21.767
>> OF COURSE NOT.

38:21.800 --> 38:23.068
WE SPOT-CHECK
OUR MANUFACTURERS' SHIPMENTS

38:23.101 --> 38:25.671
AS DOES THE CONSUMER PRODUCT
SAFETY COMMISSION.

38:25.704 --> 38:28.540
>> THEN WHY DID
THE NYPD'S CRIME LABORATORY

38:28.574 --> 38:29.975
FIND THAT THE PAINT
ON THESE TOYS

38:30.008 --> 38:32.010
CONTAINED OVER 50% LEAD?

38:36.482 --> 38:39.585
>> YOU BROUGHT ME HERE
UNDER FALSE PRETENSES.

38:39.618 --> 38:40.386
YOU LIED TO ME.

38:40.419 --> 38:42.588
>> YOU LIED
TO THE WHOLE WORLD.

38:42.621 --> 38:43.855
THESE E-MAILS
BETWEEN YOU

38:43.889 --> 38:46.558
AND YOUR CHINESE MANUFACTURER
PROVE

38:46.592 --> 38:49.461
THAT YOU KNOWINGLY POISONED
CHILDREN OVER DECADES.

38:49.495 --> 38:53.064
>> I'M DONE
ANSWERING YOUR QUESTIONS.

38:53.098 --> 38:54.533
DEFENSE IN ON YOUR LITTLE SETUP
TOO?

38:54.566 --> 38:56.001
>> SIT DOWN, SIR.
YOU'RE OUT OF ORDER.

38:56.034 --> 38:57.168
>> NO, YOU'RE OUT OF ORDER,
JUDGE,

38:57.202 --> 38:59.471
YOU AND YOUR CORRUPT D.A.,
AND YOUR JOKE OF A COURT.

38:59.505 --> 39:00.539
IF YOU THINK YOU'RE GONNA GET
AWAY WITH THIS...

39:00.572 --> 39:01.640
>> THAT'S ENOUGH.
[pounds gavel]

39:01.673 --> 39:02.941
OFFICERS, REMOVE THIS WITNESS
FROM THE COURTROOM.

39:02.974 --> 39:04.376
>> I CAN WALK
ON MY OWN.

39:04.410 --> 39:06.512
>> WE GOT IT.
WE'LL TAKE IT FROM HERE.

39:06.545 --> 39:08.480
PUT YOUR HANDS BEHIND YOUR BACK.
>> WHO THE HELL ARE YOU?

39:08.514 --> 39:12.451
>> POLICE. YOU'RE UNDER ARREST
FOR RECKLESS ENDANGERMENT.

39:16.488 --> 39:17.589
>> I'LL HAVE YOUR ASS
FOR THIS.

39:17.623 --> 39:18.924
>> I ALREADY HAVE YOURS,

39:18.957 --> 39:23.028
AND IT'S ON THE RECORD.

39:23.061 --> 39:24.229
>> JEFFREY ALLEN LYNWOOD,

39:24.262 --> 39:28.500
DO YOU HAVE ANYTHING TO SAY
BEFORE I DELIVER MY VERDICT?

39:28.534 --> 39:31.403
>> I'M SORRY, SIR.

39:31.437 --> 39:32.604
I DIDN'T MEAN
TO HURT ANYONE.

39:32.638 --> 39:34.706
>> THEN ON THE SOLE COUNT
OF MURDER IN THE SECOND DEGREE,

39:34.740 --> 39:38.910
I FIND YOU NOT GUILTY
BY REASON OF MENTAL DEFECT.

39:38.944 --> 39:41.713
AS PER THE PLEA AGREEMENT
WITH THE DISTRICT ATTORNEY,

39:41.747 --> 39:44.483
YOU WILL SURRENDER YOURSELF

39:44.516 --> 39:46.084
TO THE COMMISSIONER
OF HEALTH

39:46.117 --> 39:49.054
FOR HOSPITALIZATION
UNTIL IT IS DETERMINED

39:49.087 --> 39:52.157
THAT YOU ARE NO LONGER A THREAT
TO YOURSELF OR OTHERS.

39:52.190 --> 39:54.526
WE'RE ADJOURNED.

39:57.996 --> 39:59.465
>> BYE, MOM.
BYE, DAD.

39:59.498 --> 40:01.533
>> WE'LL BE UP TO VISIT SOON.

40:01.567 --> 40:04.570
OKAY?

40:06.838 --> 40:08.674
>> HOW LONG WILL JEFF HAVE TO BE
IN THE HOSPITAL?

40:08.707 --> 40:09.575
>> THE JUDGE HAS PROMISED
TO REVIEW HIS PROGRESS

40:09.608 --> 40:10.909
IN A MONTH.

40:10.942 --> 40:12.811
>> AND HE CAN LIVE WITH US
AFTER HE'S RELEASED?

40:12.844 --> 40:14.112
>> HE DOESN'T HAVE TO.

40:14.145 --> 40:15.581
ROWAN TOYS HAS AGREED
TO SUPPORT

40:15.614 --> 40:17.148
JEFF FINANCIALLY
FOR THE REST OF HIS LIFE.

40:17.182 --> 40:19.685
THE AGREEMENT IS BINDING,
AND THEY CAN'T BACK OUT.

40:19.718 --> 40:21.887
>> THANK YOU.

40:26.625 --> 40:28.594
>> AH, COME ON.
VOLUNTARILY PLEDGED?

40:28.627 --> 40:30.562
>> AFTER THE FEDS RECALLED
HIS TOYS,

40:30.596 --> 40:32.964
ROWAN OFFERED ME THE DEAL
SO I WOULDN'T CHARGE HIM.

40:32.998 --> 40:36.702
ONCE HE SIGNED,
I TOLD HIM TO SHOVE IT.

40:36.735 --> 40:38.737
>> YOU REALLY ARE BACK,
AREN'T YA?
